            A dedicated AI assistant for your business — answers customer questions, manages tasks, automates repetitive work, and helps you stay organized. Works across WhatsApp, Telegram, email, and more.
          </p>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:28px;">
            <span style="padding:6px 14px;background:#f1f5f9;border-radius:100px;font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--color-dark);">Customer Support</span>
            <span style="padding:6px 14px;background:#f1f5f9;border-radius:100px;font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--color-dark);">Task Automation</span>
            <span style="padding:6px 14px;background:#f1f5f9;border-radius:100px;font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--color-dark);">Multi-Platform</span>
            <span style="padding:6px 14px;background:#f1f5f9;border-radius:100px;font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--color-dark);">Bilingual</span>
